column5: headed out all by my lonesome saturday morning, i was only out for 1 1/2 hours. i hooked into 5 fish. lost 2. beautiful day, only a couple people out fishing...  couldnt ask for anything else      till next weekend!   Joe
Nice looking fish you caught there - that's great for an hour and a half of fishing!  007
I also went out this morning, and found my trib with perfect water conditions and no fish. again. for the third time this week.  I really need to find a new creek...
Nice fish and pics!  Were they hittin' the roe bags?
they all hit on pink worms..
